  "text": "These performances were successively evaluated with regard to clinical breakpoints delineating NS isolates from the susceptible (CA-SFM) ones, diameter cut-offs and specific carbapenemase detection test (Rosco test) previously published in strategies designed for screening of carbapenemase-positive isolates [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] , as well as diameter cut-offs determined in the present study by analysing the distributions of inhibition zone diameters displayed by our non-selected isolate collection (Additional file 1: Figure S1 ).",
